        <font color="white" face="Verdana, Arial, Helvetica" size="2">In early D&D games, CHA only ever affected NPC reaction and buy/sell prices.</P><P>Unless I saw a quoted statement from Verant I would be willing to guess that its the same in EQ.</P><P>A lot of opinion on things, Fear/Char, Pet XP, Stats etc seem to be 'historic fact' based on old research/Show EQ or 'something Verant maybe said'</P><P>Given that we don't know all of what exactly is changed in any Patch, I'm beginning to feel inclined to question any 'fact' regarding game play unless backed up by Verant (yes, I'm aware they get it wrong occasionally but...)</P><P>Santin</P><P> <a href="#top"><img src="icon_go_up.gif" height=15 width=15 border="0" align="right" alt="Go to Top of Page"></a></font></td>
